      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>BERSON-Samuel. 90, of Deerfield Beach, FL, originally of Brooklyn, NY. Husband of Fran for 70 years. Beloved father of Lois Markowitz (Ed) &amp; Judith Goldberg. Adored grandpa of Lisa, Amy, Suzanne &amp; Andrew. Loving great grandpa to Adam &amp; Julia, Marty &amp; Evan. Self-made success in the garment industry. Loved and respected by all who knew him.</p>
      </block>
